=梅堯臣 (1002-1060)=
==Literature==
===Monographs===
* Jonathan Chaves: Mei Yao-ch'en and the Development of Early Sung Poetry, New York: Columbia University Press, 1976
* Colin Hawes: The Social Circulation of Poetry in the Mid-Northern Song: Emotional Energy and Literati Self-Cultivation, State University of New York Press, 2005